%% Pudel Discord Message Flow v2.1.1

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Discord User
    participant Discord as Discord Gateway
    participant JDA as JDA 6
    participant Listener as DiscordEventListener
    participant Router as Message Router
    participant Prefix as Text Command
    participant AI as AI Chat
    participant Brain as PudelBrain
    participant Passive as PassiveContextProcessor

    Note over User,Passive: Message Routing Flow

    User->>Discord: Send message
    Discord->>JDA: MessageReceivedEvent
    JDA->>Listener: onMessageReceived()

    Listener->>Listener: Check if bot message
    Listener->>Listener: Check if ignored channel<br/>(guild_settings.ignored_channels)

    Listener->>Router: Route message

    alt Has Command Prefix (!)
        Router->>Prefix: CommandExecutionService
        Prefix->>Prefix: Parse command & args
        Prefix->>Prefix: Check permissions
        Prefix->>Prefix: Check cooldown
        Prefix->>Prefix: Check disabled_commands

        alt Built-in Command
            Prefix->>Prefix: Execute @TextCommand handler
        else Plugin Command
            Prefix->>Prefix: Execute plugin @TextCommand
        end

        Prefix->>Discord: Send response

    else Mention or AI Trigger
        Router->>AI: ChatbotService
        AI->>AI: Check AI enabled<br/>(guild_settings.ai_enabled)

        alt AI Enabled
            AI->>Brain: PudelBrain.process()
            Brain->>Brain: Analyze intent
            Brain->>Brain: Retrieve memory<br/>(pgvector semantic search)
            Brain->>Brain: Apply personality<br/>(biography, personality, quirks)
            Brain->>Brain: Generate response (Ollama)
            Brain-->>AI: Response text
            AI->>Discord: Send AI response
        else AI Disabled
            Note over AI: No response
        end

    else Regular Message
        Router->>Passive: PassiveContextProcessor
        Passive->>Passive: Queue message (async)
        Passive->>Passive: Batch embed + store<br/>(guild_{id}.memory_embeddings)
        Note over Passive: No direct response
    end

    Discord->>User: Display response
